<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="H" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Have-at-him" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Have-at-him,</orth> attack, thrust, stroke: <cit><quote>I'll venture one h.,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h8 2.2.85" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 II, 2, 85</bibl></cit> (cf. <cit><quote>Have</quote> <bibl n="shak. h8 2.2.1" default="NO" valid="yes">2, 1</bibl></cit>, <bibl n="shak. h8 2.2.1" default="NO" valid="yes">2, 1</bibl> F<hi rend="sub">1</hi> <emph>I'll venture one; have at him.</emph> F<hi rend="sub">2. <bibl n="shak. h8 2.2.1" default="NO" valid="yes">2, 1</bibl> 4</hi> <emph>I'll venture one heave at him</emph>).
